high_descs: Move from the bathroom,turn around and walk towards the bed.
Take the ladle from the bed.
Turn around and move towards the sidetable.
Place the ladle on the sidetable supporting the bed.
turn around and walk towards the bed once more.
Take another ladle from the bed.
Move right, then left towards the sidetable.
Place the ladle near the first one on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Move the two ladles from the bed to the side table one by one.

high_descs: Turn left, then go and stand on the right side of the bed.
Pick up the ladle near the pan.
Go to the sidetable to your left.
Put the ladle on the sidetable close to the bed.
Turn around and go right to the bed.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Go back to the sidetable.
Put the ladle next to the other ladle on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two ladles on the side table.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the bed.
Pick up the ladle from the bed on the left of the pan.
Turn right to reach the sidetable on the right of the bed.
Put the ladle on the sidetable.
Head to the bottom of the bed to face the spoon.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Head to the sidetable on the right.
Put the ladle on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two ladles on the side table.
